   Massachusetts Follows California's Lead
   And Adopts Tough Auto-Emission Rules
   ----
   By David Stipp
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
12/28/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE 34
